{"tid":1516890,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"欺凌事件發生後的政府記者會(if any","createTime":"2019-08-29T17:18:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T18:49:14.000Z","uid":121100,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"76651826e41cc518147046633b2fa31b6df7d212","tid":1516890,"uid":121100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T17:18:56.000Z","msg":"相信社會大眾都睇到近日發生為數不少針對警察子女嘅欺凌行為嘅。<br />\n<br />\n特區政府對此類事件表示強烈關注，並會與各位司局長商討對策，以求給為香港盡心盡力的各位警員及其家人，一個清靜、安全的校園環境。<br />\n<br />\n喺呢度，我對此類型嘅事件予以嚴厲譴責，並對受欺凌嘅學童及其家人致以深切嘅慰問。<br />\n<br />\n我喺度重申一次，特區政府係絕對唔希望見到任何類型嘅暴力事件發生，尤其係針對在學兒童及青少年嘅暴力行為。"},{"pid":"e14af3c3c1ab6f4f475a2efac26136b2b4d6a376","tid":1516890,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T17:19:16.000Z","msg":"有Twitter既入黎報數！Twitter要人! Twitter要人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1516761\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1516761</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n輸撚硬啦，無人做實事，文宣組幫咗你做文宣做得咁辛苦 你肯唔肯開個twitter 幫佢地？"},{"pid":"f19b59dc5a4289a0c210634975f07ce4ef75a748","tid":1516890,"uid":282289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T17:20:07.000Z","msg":"留名等睇預言成真"},{"pid":"7921314d8da5156dc8fcbf7e3d70eb14606ffa5d","tid":1516890,"uid":28921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T17:23:47.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"eb7ee23ae98fcae4dbbfcdedde40b6e64dbee05a","tid":1516890,"uid":121100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f19b59dc5a4289a0c210634975f07ce4ef75a748","tid":1516890,"uid":282289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T17:20:07.000Z","msg":"留名等睇預言成真"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T17:32:15.000Z","msg":"嚟嚟去去都係用嗰啲字眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"910a81e1b0c10d6989aa213c1bf5d11002a01c86","tid":1516890,"uid":313764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T17:51:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aVUoT4f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src